  "body": "@3xtr4t3rr3str14l Whenever you see fit, find opportunities to de-duplicate boilerplate code. For example in the test utils stubs you can define this helper function\r\n```ts\r\n// eslint-disable-next-line @typescript-eslint/ban-types\r\ntype StubbableType<TType> = Function & {prototype: TType};\r\nfunction createStubInstance<TType>(constructor: StubbableType<TType>): SinonStubbedInstance<TType> & TType {\r\n  return sinon.createStubInstance(constructor) as SinonStubbedInstance<TType> & TType;\r\n}\r\n```\r\nand initialize the class properties with just\r\n```ts\r\nthis.depositEvent = createStubInstance(DepositEventRepository);\r\n```\r\n\r\n_Originally posted by @dapplion in https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/issues/2186#issuecomment-803149369_\r\n\r\nParitcularly noticable in lodestar-beacon-state-transition",
